  3. Copy and distribute verbatim copies of the Software and this license.

  4. Study and inspect the source code for any purpose.

  5. Modify the Software and distribute Derivative Works, provided all
     conditions of this license are satisfied.

  6. Contribute modifications back to the original project under the terms
     agreed upon by the copyright holders.

